OL,5,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FA 62-year-old finance broker
OL,7,     Ffights for his life after he
OL,8,     Fsuffers a cardiac arrest while out
OL,9,     Fjogging. A 32-year-old labourer is
OL,10,     Fstabbed in the neck and abdomen
OL,11,     Foutside his home.
OL,12,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Emma McMullen has a painful
OL,14,     Fnail condition to diagnose; Dr
OL,15,     FNatalia Spierings tries to figure
OL,16,     Fout why a shoulder lump is oily;
OL,17,     Fand Dr Adil Sheraz deals with a
OL,18,     Fmole on a mole.
