OL,5,G0000 Fare Dodgers: At War with the Law
OL,6,     FInvestigators trail a man they
OL,7,     Fbelieve has racked up nearly
OL,8,     F#2,500 in unpaid fares by
OL,9,     Ffraudulently making contactless
OL,10,     Fpayments with his bank card.
OL,11,G0100 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,12,     FDr Zareena Hyder is concerned
OL,13,     Fabout a patient who's lost two
OL,14,     Fstone in six weeks, and is keen to
OL,15,     Frule out cancer. Plus, balancing
OL,16,     Fpain medication, and an alarming
OL,17,     Fasthma flare-up.
